，香港是单独关税地区，一直以来，香港对所有进口货品包括来自美国的产品都不设关税。这意味着香港也不会跟随内地向美国加征 34% 关税。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6f4401670611af12608131c9132b23b2_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "226 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1892868985126626712"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIuuHkup7IvoZXEAMaCTExNDM4NDQzMSD98tG/BjAAOIsBQAdyEzE4OTI4Njg5ODUxMjY2MjY3MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1744094068.133320", "card_id": "Q_14063490054", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 65}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "世界关税大战开启，全球经济会崩溃吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e01ad0311f79a19e13bc621074e0fe67_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "214 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/14063490054"}}, "attached_info": "CkIIuuHkup7IvoZXEAMaCTExMzc4ODA3NiDp9Zu+BjAAOLEBQAhyCzE0MDYzNDkwMDU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1744094068.134126", "card_id": "Q_1892575268201259098", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「短剧一哥」柯淳自曝片酬「日薪 2 万元」，拍短剧这么赚钱吗？目前短剧演员片酬行情如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，在综艺《无限超越班 3》中，当被问到拍短剧的片酬，短剧演员柯淳称：「我们是按天算的，我虽然现在是 2 万，但是还没有接过 2 万的。」 据公开资料，柯淳，本名赵柯淳，2000 年 10 月 28 日出生于湖南省岳阳市，中国内地男演员。 此前其主演的短剧作品《好一个乖乖女》总观看量突破 20 亿，微博话题阅读量达 1.8 亿。赵柯淳一周涨粉超 150 万，被称为短剧赛道「顶流级」演员之一。「短剧一哥」柯淳自曝片酬：我们是按天算的，日薪 2 万元"}, "image_area": {"url": " https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3b613f